Class AnimalFactory

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.factory.BaseFactory<Animal>
cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.factory.AnimalFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Factory<Animal>
public class AnimalFactory extends BaseFactory<Animal>
This class is a factory for creating Animal objects. It extends the BaseFactory and registers the supported animal types, such as cow, chicken, sheep, and pig. It provides the functionality to create an animal of a specified type.
